39
0:01:57.734,000 --> 0:01:58,000
I learned from them.

40
0:01:59.084,000 --> 0:02:,000
It's the story of planning,

41
0:02:00.887,000 --> 0:02:03,000
the story of the formation of the planning profession.

42
0:02:04.151,000 --> 0:02:08,000
When in the 19th century people were choking

43
