46
0:02:19.334,000 --> 0:02:2,000
and we like to say

47
0:02:20.509,000 --> 0:02:23,000
the planners have been trying to repeat that experience ever since.

48
0:02:23.725,000 --> 0:02:25,000
So there's the onset of what we call Euclidean zoning,

49
