184
0:08:01.913,000 --> 0:08:02,000
This is Portland, Oregon,

185
0:08:03.284,000 --> 0:08:06,000
famously 200-foot blocks, famously walkable.

186
0:08:06.874,000 --> 0:08:07,000
This is Salt Lake City,

187
0:08:08.216,000 --> 0:08:1,000
famously 600-foot blocks,

188
0:08:10.32,000 --> 0:08:11,000
famously unwalkable.

189
0:08:11.713,000 --> 0:08:14,000
If you look at the two, it's almost like two different planets,

190
0:08:14.743,000 --> 0:08:16,000
but these places were both built by humans

191
0:08:17.083,000 --> 0:08:2,000
and in fact, the story is that when you have a 200-foot block city,

192
0:08:20.747,000 --> 0:08:21,000
